import { GraphQLModule } from '@graphql-modules/core'
import typeDefs from './typeDefs'
import resolver from './resolvers'
import User from '../../mongoose-models/User'

const user = new GraphQLModule({
  typeDefs,
  resolvers: resolver,
  context: (ctx) => ({ token: ctx.token, User }),
})

export default user

export const USER_NOT_FOUND = 'USER not found'
export const USER_EDITED_SUCCESSFULLY = 'USER edited successfully'
export const USER_ALREADY_DELETED = 'USER is already deleted'
export const USER_DELETED_SUCCESSFULLY = 'USER deleted successfully'
export const INVALID_CREDENTIALS = 'invalid credentials'
export const LOGGED_IN_SUCCESSFULLY = 'logged in successfully'
export const UNAUTHORIZED = 'unauthorized'
export const SERVER_ERROR = 'server error'
